node.text: 2017 playoffs in Calgary with the Budweiser team.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SIGNED capit capitels ALEX OVECHKIN 5 YEARS, $47.5M ($9.5M AAV) capitals lals WASHINGTON HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: Alex Ovechkin is signing a five-year extension with the Washington Capitals.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'SIGNED NYR 99 BaUeR PAVEL BUCHNEVICH YEARS, $23.2M RAM ($5.8M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: Pavel Buchnevich has signed a four-year deal with the St. Louis Blues.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 27, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, people playing hockey and text that says 'SIGNED DIZONA CCM 3 CONOR GARLAND Yanea AR 5 YEARS, $24.75M ($4.95M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: Conor Garland has signed a five-year deal with the Vancouver Canucks.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 27, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Allan Walsh @walsha While Marc-A Andre Fleury still hasn't heard from anybody with the Vegas Golden Knights, he has apparently been traded to Chicago. Marc-Andre will be taking time to discuss his situation with his family and seriously evaluate his hockey future at this time. 12:05 PM 2021-07-27 Twitter for iPhone HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

Photo by Hockey Collective on July 27, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Jesse Granger @JesseGranger_ A source close to Marc- Marc-Andre Fleury says that the trade is done, and that the Vezina Trophy winner found out through Twitter. #VegasBorn 11:41 AM 2021-07-27 TweetDeck HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

Photo by Hockey Collective on July 27, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'TRADE CHI RECEIVES .MARC-ANDRE FLEURY VGK VGKRECEIVES RECEIVES .FUTURE CONSIDERATIONS CCM H EMILY KAPLAN HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text:
The Vegas Golden Knights have dealt the 2021 Vezina winner. This clears $7M of cap space for the Golden Knights.

Update: the player going to Vegas is forward Mikael Hakkarainen.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 26, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text.

node.text: Brenden Dillon goes to the Jets for a couple 2nd rounders. The picks are in 2022 & 2023.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 26, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, playing a sport and text that says 'SIGNED FLORIDA JARRIOR ORIDA SAM BENNETT WARA BaUeR YEARS, $17.6M ($4.4M AAV) HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: Sam Bennett cashes in on a new four-year deal with the Panthers.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 25, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'NEWS HOCKEY COLLECTIVE A T DEFENSEMAN NIKLAS HJALMARSSON IS RETIRING FROM THE NHL H/T: CRAIG MORGAN'.

node.text: The 34 year old is a three time Stanley Cup Champion with the Blackhawks and has spent the last 4 seasons with the Coyotes.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 25, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'NEWS HOCKEY COLLECTIVE A T DEFENSEMAN NIKLAS HJALMARSSON IS RETIRING FROM THE NHL H/T: CRAIG MORGAN'.
Photo by Hockey Collective on July 25, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and indoor.
Photo shared by Hockey Collective on July 24, 2021 tagging @_quinnhughes, @lhughes_06, and @jackhughes. May be an image of 3 people and people standing.

node.text: Three brothers, all top 10 draft picks. Incredible!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 24, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'TRADE 23 HOCKEY COLLECTIVE CCM FLORIDA RECEIVES SAM REINHART RECEIVES 20221STD 1ST RD PICK DEVON LEVI'.

node.text: Sam Reinhart is headed to Florida.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Hockey Collective on July 24, 2021. May be an image of 2 people and text that says 'TRADE RECEIVES P CAM ATKINSON RECEIVES JAKUB VORACEK ELLIOTTE FRIEDMAN HOCKEY COLLECTIVE'.

node.text: The trade is one for one.
